overview: After being absent for 17 years, Jacques Vermeire returns back to the theater for his 5th comedy show. 5 to 12 premieres on Wednesday October 31st 2012 with an extended introduction-weekend in the Arendberg concert hall in Antwerp, Belgium.  Expectations are higher than ever. Jacques Vermeire proves in 5 to 12 that he's still that long-missed stand-up comedian his fans had to wait for so long. Back with his hilarious characters, such as Fonske Verzele. But he's also reinventing himself in a night full of show and face-making stories and sketches.
tagline: After 17 years Jacques Vermeire is back with a whole new stand-up comedy-show
title: Jacques Vermeire: 5 To 12
